ConstraintError.desc: A mutation operation in a transaction failed because a constraint was not satisfied.
ConstraintError.name: ConstraintError

DataCloneError.desc: The object can not be cloned.
DataCloneError.name: DataCloneError

EncodingError.desc: The encoding operation (either encoded or decoding) failed.
EncodingError.name: EncodingError

HierarchyRequestError.desc: The operation would yield an incorrect node tree.
HierarchyRequestError.name: HierarchyRequestError

IndexSizeError.desc: The index is not in the allowed range.
IndexSizeError.name: IndexSizeError

InvalidAccessError.desc: The object does not support the operation or argument.
InvalidAccessError.name: InvalidAccessError

InvalidModificationError.desc: The object can not be modified in this way.
InvalidModificationError.name: InvalidModificationError

InvalidNodeTypeError.desc: The supplied node is incorrect or has an incorrect ancestor for this operation.
InvalidNodeTypeError.name: InvalidNodeTypeError

InvalidStateError.desc: The object is in an invalid state.
InvalidStateError.name: InvalidStateError

NamespaceError.desc: The operation is not allowed by Namespaces in XML.
NamespaceError.name: NamespaceError

NoModificationAllowedError.desc: The object can not be modified.
NoModificationAllowedError.name: NoModificationAllowedError

NotFoundError.desc: The object can not be found here.
NotFoundError.name: NotFoundError

OperationError.desc: The operation failed for an operation-specific reason.
OperationError.name: OperationError

ReadOnlyError.desc: The mutating operation was attempted in a "readonly" transaction.
ReadOnlyError.name: ReadOnlyError

SyntaxError.desc: The string did not match the expected pattern.
SyntaxError.name: SyntaxError

TransactionInactiveError.desc: A request was placed against a transaction which is currently not active, or which is finished.
TransactionInactiveError.name: TransactionInactiveError

URLMismatchError.desc: The given URL does not match another URL.
URLMismatchError.name: URLMismatchError

UnknownError.desc: The operation failed for an unknown transient reason (e.g. out of memory).
UnknownError.name: UnknownError

VersionError.desc: An attempt was made to open a database using a lower version than the existing version.
VersionError.name: VersionError

WrongDocumentError.desc: The object is in the wrong document.
WrongDocumentError.name: WrongDocumentError
